          hr.my-6

        .border-bottom.border-300.pb-6.mb-6
          .row.justify-content-center
            .col-lg-4
              h3 Senior Designer
            .col
              p.mb-0 Maecenas sed diam eget risus varius blandit sit amet non magna. Donec id elit non mi porta gravida at eget metus. Aenean lacinia bibendum nulla sed consectetur.

              h5.text-uppercase.ls.mt-5 Eligibility
              ul
                li Sed posuere consectetur est at lobortis
                li Morbi leo risus, porta ac consectetur ac, vestibulum at eros
                li Aenean lacinia bibendum nulla sed consectetur

        .border-bottom.border-300.pb-6.mb-6
          .row.justify-content-center
            .col-lg-4
              h3 Photographer
            .col
              p.mb-0 Integer posuere erat a ante venenatis dapibus posuere velit aliquet. Curabitur blandit tempus porttitor. Nullam quis risus eget urna mollis ornare vel eu leo. Donec sed odio dui. Nulla vitae elit libero, a pharetra augue.

              h5.text-uppercase.ls.mt-5 Eligibility
              ul
                li Cras mattis consectetur purus sit amet fermentum
                li Pellentesque ornare sem lacinia quam venenatis vestibulum
                li Vestibulum id ligula porta felis euismod semper

        .row.justify-content-center
          .col-lg-4
            h3 Apply for The Job
          .col
            form.mt-3
              .row
                .col-sm-6.col-md-5.col-lg-4.col-xl-3
                  label.form-label Position *
                  select.form-select
                    option Senior Architect
                    option Architect
                    option Senior Designer
                    option Designer
                    option Business Development
                    option Photographer
                    option IT Manager
                    option Office Manager
                .col-12.mt-4
                  input.form-control(type="hidden" name="to" value="user@domain.extension")
                  label.form-label Email *
                  input(type="email" placeholder="" required).form-control
                .col-lg-6.mt-4
                  label.form-label Name *
                  input(type="text" placeholder="" required).form-control
                  small First Name
                .col-lg-6.mt-4
                  label.form-label &nbsp;
                  input(type="text" placeholder="" required).form-control
                  small Last Name
                .col-12.mt-4
                  label.form-label Cover Letter *
                  textarea(rows="8" placeholder="" required).form-control
                .col-12.mt-4
                  button.btn.btn-md-lg.btn-primary(type="Submit") 
                    span.color-white.fw-600 Submit
